flowchart TB
  %% Salesforce Lead Assignment Template
  %% Customize criteria and routing rules based on your org

  Start((New Lead)) --> CheckSource{Lead Source?}

  CheckSource -->|Website| WebLead[Web Lead]
  CheckSource -->|Event| EventLead[Event Lead]
  CheckSource -->|Referral| ReferralLead[Referral Lead]
  CheckSource -->|Other| OtherLead[Other Source]

  WebLead --> CheckScore{Lead Score?}
  EventLead --> CheckScore
  ReferralLead --> Priority[High Priority]
  OtherLead --> CheckScore

  CheckScore -->|Score >= 80| Hot[Hot Lead]
  CheckScore -->|Score 50-79| Warm[Warm Lead]
  CheckScore -->|Score < 50| Cold[Cold Lead]

  Hot --> CheckTerritory{Territory?}
  Warm --> CheckTerritory
  Cold --> NurtureQueue[Nurture Queue]
  Priority --> SeniorRep[Senior Sales Rep]

  CheckTerritory -->|Enterprise| EnterpriseTeam[Enterprise Team]
  CheckTerritory -->|Mid-Market| MidMarketTeam[Mid-Market Team]
  CheckTerritory -->|SMB| SMBTeam[SMB Team]

  EnterpriseTeam --> RoundRobin[Round Robin Assignment]
  MidMarketTeam --> RoundRobin
  SMBTeam --> RoundRobin

  RoundRobin --> NotifyRep[Notify Assigned Rep]
  SeniorRep --> NotifyRep
  NurtureQueue --> AutomatedCampaign[Automated Email Campaign]

  NotifyRep --> End((Lead Assigned))
  AutomatedCampaign --> End
